channel.title: Everyone look here relates to steve irwin
channel.description:
ok everyone knows how he died and everything and i just caught up with my godmothers husband who was steve's cameraman while he was filming his documentry so i will be getting some videos and pictures of steve before diveing and during diving. he is coming over next week if people wanna know about this. ill release some things that i get but some of the really sad stuff i wont put up when i get thanks.
update:
i talked to him on the phone and he actually was the person filming steve while at batt reef when steve "met the stingray" when the stingray got him steve straight away pulled out the stinger and then he sank to the bottom needing oxygen. the production was made up by his daughter bindi and it was her idea to do a underwater documentry. hes coming over in a few more days and unlike many people im awaiting the images and recordings.
danieb
